 per unit for each product using traditional absorption costing.\"\"\",9\n1493,\"\"\"EVALUATING THE IMPACT OF ACTIVITY-BASED COSTING ON PRICING STRATEGIES AT BBB\"\"\",\"\"\"COST OF A GC USING ACTIVITY-BASED COSTING\"\"\",\"\"\"The case of Evaluating the Impact of Activity-Based Costing on Pricing Strategies at BBB includes the calculation of the cost of a GC using activity-based costing.\"\"\",8\n1494,\"\"\"EVALUATING THE IMPACT OF ACTIVITY-BASED COSTING ON PRICING STRATEGIES AT BBB\"\"\",\"\"\"COST PER UNIT OF A TYPICAL EX USING ACTIVITY-BASED COSTING\"\"\",\"\"\"The case of Evaluating the Impact of Activity-Based Costing on Pricing Strategies at BBB includes the calculation of the cost per unit of a typical EX using activity-based costing.\"\"\",8\n1491,\"\"\"EVALUATING THE IMPACT OF ACTIVITY-BASED COSTING ON PRICING STRATEGIES AT BBB\"\"\",\"\"\"CURRENT METHOD OF ABSORBING OVERHEADS\"\"\",\"\"\"The case of Evaluating the Impact of Activity-Based Costing on Pricing Strategies at BBB discusses the current method of absorbing overheads at BBB.\"\"\",8\n1492,\"\"\"EVALUATING THE IMPACT OF ACTIVITY-BASED COSTING ON PRICING STRATEGIES AT BBB\"\"\",\"\"\"SALES PRICE FOR A TYPICAL GC USING CURRENT METHOD\"\"\",\"\"\"The case of Evaluating the Impact of Activity-Based Costing on Pricing Strategies at BBB includes the calculation of the sales price for a typical GC using the current method of absorbing overheads.\"\"\",8\n1495,\"\"\"EVALUATING THE IMPACT OF ACTIVITY-BASED COSTING ON PRICING STRATEGIES AT BBB\"\"\",\"\"\"QUIZ ON ACTIVITY-BASED COSTING AT BBB\"\"\",\"\"\"The case of Evaluating the Impact of Activity-Based Costing on Pricing Strategies at BBB includes a quiz on activity-based costing at BBB.\"\"\",8\n234,\"\"\"FIXED PRODUCTION OVERHEADS\"\"\",\"\"\"SALES PRICE AND QUANTITY VARIANCES ANALYSIS FOR BLOCK CO\"\"\",\"\"\"Block Co allocates fixed production overheads based on machine hours.\"\"\",8\n135,\"\"\"TRADITIONAL ABSORPTION COSTING\"\"\",\"\"\"LABOR HOURS\